list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: New method of making a random point of String, this time i use String.format to make a CELL instead of combining a Char and a Integer. New method: " cell = String.format("%c%d",startRow,startColumn);". Instead of: " cell = (char) startRow + Integer.toString(startColumn);". The output is still the same, just a different way making it.
